{"tid":1431753,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【九唔搭八】留言「搵唔到生存原因」 鍾鎮濤大仔擬賣名表套現","createTime":"2019-08-08T05:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T06:06:45.000Z","uid":175314,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"42a8429c0b3e28aadccc8519b6aeb861af6b1c8e","tid":1431753,"uid":175314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:19:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://today.line.me/HK/article/55olWx?utm_source=copyshare\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2FHK%2Farticle%2F55olWx%3Futm_source%3Dcopyshare&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=18747339\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/HK/article/55olWx?utm_source=copyshare</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NnTudPd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNnTudPd.jpg&h=657e14b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾鎮濤與前妻章小蕙所生的29歲長子鍾嘉浚移居美國多年，間中返港與家人團聚。鍾嘉浚近日在個人社交網站發文，直言「活在殭屍般的生活」，指自己生活得不開心，以英文寫上：「看不到生存的原因。」，據悉，父親鍾鎮濤曾回覆傳媒指「多謝關心」。<br />\n鍾嘉浚在Facebook發文，以英文寫，「坦白說，我找不到任何生存的理由。我在現時的生活中找不到任何我喜歡的事，就像殭屍一樣般生活。當然，我曾經有過美好時光，但過去一年又一年不斷經歷各種痛苦，希望有好的事情發生來喚醒我。」<br />\n之後他再發放一張手錶照片，指2019是他人生中最差勁的一年，「被一班人搞亂了他的人生。」要賣掉自己第一隻名表解決問題。未知父親鍾鎮濤將如何陪兒子渡過難關呢？據悉，有傳媒曾聯絡鍾鎮濤，他回覆指，「兒子已經29歲，有自己的世界」，並多謝大家關心。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8491cf77efdee340844042a72aa2c0379638efa3","tid":1431753,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"移居美國 仆街仔 你係咩人，你老豆係咩人移居美國 食屎狗"},{"pid":"f0e0550590ad3f1f0ddcc36191e4d02aa51b5ebe","tid":1431753,"uid":175314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8491cf77efdee340844042a72aa2c0379638efa3","tid":1431753,"uid":10757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T05:54:55.000Z","msg":"移居美國 仆街仔 你係咩人，你老豆係咩人移居美國 食屎狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:06:45.000Z","msg":"瘟乸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}